who's the only one who has worked hard?

504
00:33:32,750 --> 00:33:34,375
You shut the fuck up!

505
00:33:34,458 --> 00:33:35,666
I won't shut up!

506
00:33:35,750 --> 00:33:37,625
Tell me which part isn't true?

507
00:33:37,708 --> 00:33:40,041
The fact that Sak
is the only one working hard,

508
00:33:40,125 --> 00:33:42,583
