are having an affair!?

509
00:33:43,291 --> 00:33:46,291
You're fucking crazy!
Come, Grandma. I'll take you to bed.

510
00:33:46,375 --> 00:33:49,333
If you don't get real,
I'll tell the police.

511
00:33:50,958 --> 00:33:52,041
Go ahead!

512
00:33:52,750 --> 00:33:54,750
And you think Pa will thank you

513
00:33:54,833 --> 00:33:57,791
for dragging his favorite grandson
into trouble?

514
00:33:57,875 --> 00:33:59,875
Sure. Come on, Ma.

515
00:34:02,333 --> 00:34:03,958
Such a pain in the ass.

516
00:34:23,625 --> 00:34:27,333
WHAT ARE THE POLICE SO SCARED OFF?

517
00:34:29,291 --> 00:34:32,083
You're about to retire.
Why bother with this case?

518
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:36,541
Look. So many people
making their own judgment.

519
00:34:36,625 --> 00:34:37,625
They're all crazy.

